- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep generative encoder-decoder models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with natural language generation and image understanding. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with multi-modal vision and language tasks.
